{"tid":357534,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓人買金避險　即食食品大賣","createTime":"2017-08-13T03:16:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-13T05:05:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7a6b104c70332fcdcca2ca4c98fcaf4f2b511e92","tid":357534,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20120051&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170813\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20120051%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170813&d=qLfabYGr96qrIYdSPxS63tibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=60cf4511\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20120051%26category_guid%3D15335%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170813&h=bb8954b5\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20120051&amp;category_guid=15335&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170813</a><br />\n<br />\n南韓人買金避險　即食食品大賣<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n首爾一個用作緊急庇護點的地鐵站，貯存了救援物資。路透社<br />\n<br />\n本已對北韓恐嚇麻木的南韓人，近日開始有所準備，買黃金避險的人飆升四倍，即食食品銷量亦大增50%。當局計劃本月23日舉行全國民防演習，但很多民眾根本不知道避難場所地點。<br />\n大邱即食食品公司「Combat Ration」過去一周的銷情比過往大增50%。其他即食食品公司和網購公司均表示，即食食品的銷量上升了，相信是與朝鮮半島局勢緊張有關。南韓黃金交易所3M亦指上周金條銷量由每日50條升至250條。<br />\nCombat Ration總裁尹希列（音譯）表示：「我感覺到今次有所不同。自2006年北韓首次核試後，從未有過如這樣的反應，因為人們都對北韓核試和試射導彈的頻密程度麻木了。」<br />\n<br />\n月底全國民防演習<br />\n<br />\n南韓本月23日將舉行全國演習，首爾全部25個地區將會參與，而去年僅得5個地區參與。整個演習歷時5分鐘，屆時電台將發放警笛、某些地點禁止汽車通行，民眾須走到附近地鐵站等防空洞或安全地點。<br />\n不過，路透社到首爾兩個地鐵站調查，發現大部份人根本不知地鐵站是市內3,200個安全地點之一。另外，由於缺乏政府援助，很多被列為安全地點的建築並未存有足夠食物、食水或醫療用品等。<br />\n路透社<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n北韓籌謀海上試射導彈<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n關島發應對導彈小冊子教逃生<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;5小時前<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n美朝連日互兇　局勢隨時惡化習勸特朗普勿再挑釁北韓<br />\n<br />\n國際要聞&nbsp;5小時前"},{"pid":"d111d647b7c3a08da510eaa049cb5b6175e1955b","tid":357534,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:17:19.000Z","msg":"可以走金去韓國啦"},{"pid":"f8af849f1e977de626eb3d7fab007bb9d689338e","tid":357534,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170813/large/13we8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170813%2Flarge%2F13we8p.jpg&h=4626d58a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首爾一個用作緊急庇護點的地鐵站，貯存了救援物資。路透社"},{"pid":"2999d739ee33a6cb11b5e13513d624eef8c0e766","tid":357534,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:35:54.000Z","msg":"午餐肉"},{"pid":"273e2c3b38741993ff5fff51c2e370f6c18dfe5b","tid":357534,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:45:35.000Z","msg":"瘋狂食部隊鍋"},{"pid":"f442dc92604476f79e17959c144460711554b2d4","tid":357534,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:47:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20170813/large/13we8p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170813%2Flarge%2F13we8p.jpg&h=4626d58a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首爾一個用作緊急庇護點的地鐵站，貯存了救援物資。路透社</blockquote><br />\n中國應該見唔到咁既野"},{"pid":"001cf98d1b8584da63a1de0d0d38fe985529e131","tid":357534,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:51:02.000Z","msg":"泡菜仔都手持緊午餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"685125c3ffc105c4d689edecd805ed205ca96fcf","tid":357534,"uid":51200,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-13T03:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img sr